      "content_html": "\u003ch2\u003eNavigation\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/documentation/en-us/unreal-engine/API\"\u003eUnreal Engine C++ API Reference\u003c/a\u003e \u003e \u003ca href=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/documentation/en-us/unreal-engine/API/Plugins\"\u003ePlugins\u003c/a\u003e \u003e \u003ca href=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/documentation/en-us/unreal-engine/API/Plugins/ChaosClothAsset\"\u003eChaosClothAsset\u003c/a\u003e \u003e \u003ca href=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/documentation/en-us/unreal-engine/API/Plugins/ChaosClothAsset/ChaosClothAsset\"\u003eChaosClothAsset\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch2\u003eReferences\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003ctable\u003e\n  \u003cthead\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003cth\u003e \u003c/th\u003e\n      \u003cth\u003e \u003c/th\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n  \u003c/thead\u003e\n  \u003ctbody\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eModule\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/documentation/en-us/unreal-engine/API/Plugins/ChaosClothAsset\"\u003eChaosClothAsset\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eHeader\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e/Engine/Plugins/ChaosClothAsset/Source/ChaosClothAsset/Public/ChaosClothAsset/ClothGeometryTools.h\u003c/td\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eInclude\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e#include \"ChaosClothAsset/ClothGeometryTools.h\"\u003c/td\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n  \u003c/tbody\u003e\n\u003c/table\u003e\n\n\u003ch2\u003eSyntax\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cpre\u003e\u003ccode\u003estruct FClothGeometryTools  \n\u003c/code\u003e\u003c/pre\u003e\n\n\u003ch2\u003eRemarks\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eGeometry tools operating on cloth collections.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch2\u003eFunctions\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\n\u003ctable\u003e\n  \u003cthead\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003cth\u003e \u003c/th\u003e\n      \u003cth\u003eType\u003c/th\u003e\n      \u003cth\u003eName\u003c/th\u003e\n      \u003cth\u003eDescription\u003c/th\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n  \u003c/thead\u003e\n  \u003ctbody\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/bcaade5b-8163-42d4-ab7c-e2c6fcf51459/api_function_public.png\" alt=\"Public function\" loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Public function\" convert=\"false\" width=\"18\" /\u003e \u003cimg src=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/e235a1df-4b5b-4d13-88ec-28a985503b8a/api_function_static.png\" alt=\"Static\" loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Static\" convert=\"false\" width=\"18\" /\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003evoid\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/documentation/en-us/unreal-engine/API/Plugins/ChaosClothAsset/ChaosClothAsset/FClothGeometryTools/BindMeshToRootBo-\"\u003eBindMeshToRootBone\u003c/a\u003e\n (\nconst TSharedRef\u003c FManagedArrayCollection \u003e\u0026 ClothCollection,\u003cbr\u003e\nbool bBindSimMesh,\u003cbr\u003e\nbool bBindRenderMesh\u003cbr\u003e\n )\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eSet the skinning weights for all of the sim/render vertices in ClothCollection to be bound to the root node.\u003c/td\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/5dba8434-54b7-40d8-980a-736c964d375f/api_function_public.png\" alt=\"Public function\" loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Public function\" convert=\"false\" width=\"18\" /\u003e \u003cimg src=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/5a1dfeb7-8590-4c55-a39a-5e3da948f8b3/api_function_static.png\" alt=\"Static\" loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Static\" convert=\"false\" width=\"18\" /\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003evoid\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/documentation/en-us/unreal-engine/API/Plugins/ChaosClothAsset/ChaosClothAsset/FClothGeometryTools/BuildConnectedSe-\"\u003eBuildConnectedSeams\u003c/a\u003e\n (\nconst TArray\u003c FIntVector2 \u003e\u0026 InputStitches,\u003cbr\u003e\nconst UE::Geometry::FDynamicMesh3\u0026 Mesh,\u003cbr\u003e\nTArray\u003c TArray\u003c FIntVector2 \u003e \u003e\u0026 Seams\u003cbr\u003e\n )\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eFind sets of connected stitches for the input stitches given in random order.\u003c/td\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/6a3d6e1b-adf9-4a60-bf4d-df0a6fecbcde/api_function_public.png\" alt=\"Public function\" loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Public function\" convert=\"false\" width=\"18\" /\u003e \u003cimg src=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/36b899c4-dc5f-4389-8b5d-f8357201449e/api_function_static.png\" alt=\"Static\" loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Static\" convert=\"false\" width=\"18\" /\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003evoid\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/documentation/en-us/unreal-engine/API/Plugins/ChaosClothAsset/ChaosClothAsset/FClothGeometryTools/BuildConnectedSe-_1\"\u003eBuildConnectedSeams2D\u003c/a\u003e\n (\nconst TSharedRef\u003c const FManagedArrayCollection \u003e\u0026 ClothCollection,\u003cbr\u003e\nint32 SeamIndex,\u003cbr\u003e\nconst UE::Geometry::FDynamicMesh3\u0026 Mesh,\u003cbr\u003e\nTArray\u003c TArray\u003c FIntVector2 \u003e \u003e\u0026 Seams\u003cbr\u003e\n )\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eFind sets of connected stitches for the given seam.\u003c/td\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/df160c15-a157-4683-917d-295d41480e1f/api_function_public.png\" alt=\"Public function\" loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Public function\" convert=\"false\" width=\"18\" /\u003e \u003cimg src=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/ee7205c0-77c1-4957-a942-7c847c4ac16a/api_function_static.png\" alt=\"Static\" loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Static\" convert=\"false\" width=\"18\" /\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003evoid\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/documentation/en-us/unreal-engine/API/Plugins/ChaosClothAsset/ChaosClothAsset/FClothGeometryTools/BuildSimMeshFrom-_1\"\u003eBuildSimMeshFromDynamicMesh\u003c/a\u003e\n (\nconst TSharedRef\u003c FManagedArrayCollection \u003e\u0026 ClothCollection,\u003cbr\u003e\nconst UE::Geometry::FDynamicMesh3\u0026 DynamicMesh,\u003cbr\u003e\nint32 UVChannelIndex,\u003cbr\u003e\nconst FVector2f\u0026 UVScale,\u003cbr\u003e\nbool bAppend,\u003cbr\u003e\nbool bImportNormals\u003cbr\u003e\n )\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eUnwrap and build SimMesh data from a DynamicMesh Normals are only imported if the DynamicMesh has both a UVOverlay and a NormalOverlay\u003c/td\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/3e13a867-8614-43a5-ae82-d99bf048b567/api_function_public.png\" alt=\"Public function\" loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Public function\" convert=\"false\" width=\"18\" /\u003e \u003cimg src=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/86d9c39a-afa0-4773-b714-67a9397a3a0e/api_function_static.png\" alt=\"Static\" loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Static\" convert=\"false\" width=\"18\" /\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003evoid\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/documentation/en-us/unreal-engine/API/Plugins/ChaosClothAsset/ChaosClothAsset/FClothGeometryTools/BuildSimMeshFrom-\"\u003eBuildSimMeshFromDynamicMeshes\u003c/a\u003e\n (\nconst TSharedRef\u003c FManagedArrayCollection \u003e\u0026 ClothCollection,\u003cbr\u003e\nconst UE::Geometry::FDynamicMesh3\u0026 Mesh2D,\u003cbr\u003e\nconst UE::Geometry::FDynamicMesh3\u0026 Mesh3D,\u003cbr\u003e\nint32 PatternIndexLayerId,\u003cbr\u003e\nbool bTransferWeightMaps,\u003cbr\u003e\nbool bTransferSimSkinningData,\u003cbr\u003e\nbool bAppend,\u003cbr\u003e\nTMap\u003c int, int32 \u003e\u0026 OutDynamicMeshToClothVertexMap\u003cbr\u003e\n )\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eBuild (or add to) a ClothCollection Sim Mesh from the given 2D and 3D mesh data.\u003c/td\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/f36890b2-e1d4-4562-aa11-3c540dfbf95a/api_function_public.png\" alt=\"Public function\" loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Public function\" convert=\"false\" width=\"18\" /\u003e \u003cimg src=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/cfd5502b-a76a-4df4-8f80-92b6711942a8/api_function_static.png\" alt=\"Static\" loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Static\" convert=\"false\" width=\"18\" /\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003evoid\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/documentation/en-us/unreal-engine/API/Plugins/ChaosClothAsset/ChaosClothAsset/FClothGeometryTools/CleanupAndCompac-\"\u003eCleanupAndCompactMesh\u003c/a\u003e\n (\nconst TSharedRef\u003c FManagedArrayCollection \u003e\u0026 ClothCollection\u003cbr\u003e\n )\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eRemove (topologically) degenerate triangles.\u003c/td\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/29df9a2b-2ce2-4d8e-b107-efe594165715/api_function_public.png\" alt=\"Public function\" loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Public function\" convert=\"false\" width=\"18\" /\u003e \u003cimg src=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/5a3caff9-8adf-49ee-94b5-f39c5358a983/api_function_static.png\" alt=\"Static\" loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Static\" convert=\"false\" width=\"18\" /\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003ebool\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/documentation/en-us/unreal-engine/API/Plugins/ChaosClothAsset/ChaosClothAsset/FClothGeometryTools/ConvertSelection-/1\"\u003eConvertSelectionToNewGroupType\u003c/a\u003e\n (\nconst TSharedRef\u003c const FManagedArrayCollection \u003e\u0026 ClothCollection,\u003cbr\u003e\nconst FName\u0026 SelectionName,\u003cbr\u003e\nconst FName\u0026 GroupName,\u003cbr\u003e\nTSet\u003c int32 \u003e\u0026 OutSelectionSet\u003cbr\u003e\n )\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eGet a copy of the selection, converting to the desired group if possible.\u003c/td\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/61773385-25bd-4ffa-b2db-311706d0c0fc/api_function_public.png\" alt=\"Public function\" loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Public function\" convert=\"false\" width=\"18\" /\u003e \u003cimg src=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/f68fd696-7898-4a93-9259-b07206feb2b9/api_function_static.png\" alt=\"Static\" loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Static\" convert=\"false\" width=\"18\" /\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003ebool\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/documentation/en-us/unreal-engine/API/Plugins/ChaosClothAsset/ChaosClothAsset/FClothGeometryTools/ConvertSelection-/2\"\u003eConvertSelectionToNewGroupType\u003c/a\u003e\n (\nconst TSharedRef\u003c const FManagedArrayCollection \u003e\u0026 ClothCollection,\u003cbr\u003e\nconst FName\u0026 SelectionName,\u003cbr\u003e\nconst FName\u0026 GroupName,\u003cbr\u003e\nbool bSecondarySelection,\u003cbr\u003e\nTSet\u003c int32 \u003e\u0026 OutSelectionSet\u003cbr\u003e\n )\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eGet a copy of the selection, converting to the desired group if possible.\u003c/td\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/1d2c3e01-71b3-4629-8a51-5fce97f650d9/api_function_public.png\" alt=\"Public function\" loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Public function\" convert=\"false\" width=\"18\" /\u003e \u003cimg src=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/140965f0-51e9-47b1-8e46-bd56f07ee138/api_function_static.png\" alt=\"Static\" loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Static\" convert=\"false\" width=\"18\" /\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003evoid\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/documentation/en-us/unreal-engine/API/Plugins/ChaosClothAsset/ChaosClothAsset/FClothGeometryTools/CopySimMeshToRen-\"\u003eCopySimMeshToRenderMesh\u003c/a\u003e\n (\nconst TSharedRef\u003c FManagedArrayCollection \u003e\u0026 ClothCollection,\u003cbr\u003e\nconst FString\u0026 RenderMaterialPathName,\u003cbr\u003e\nbool bSingleRenderPattern\u003cbr\u003e\n )\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eTurn the sim mesh portion of this ClothCollection into a render mesh.\u003c/td\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/99c1614e-0e3d-4c94-aee9-72bce67ad86d/api_function_public.png\" alt=\"Public function\" loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Public function\" convert=\"false\" width=\"18\" /\u003e \u003cimg src=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/de0f3631-8bac-4624-a557-52120837de8a/api_function_static.png\" alt=\"Static\" loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Static\" convert=\"false\" width=\"18\" /\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003evoid\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/documentation/en-us/unreal-engine/API/Plugins/ChaosClothAsset/ChaosClothAsset/FClothGeometryTools/DeleteRenderMesh\"\u003eDeleteRenderMesh\u003c/a\u003e\n (\nconst TSharedRef\u003c FManagedArrayCollection \u003e\u0026 ClothCollection\u003cbr\u003e\n )\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eDelete the render mesh data.\u003c/td\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/81c975f8-a8a0-4ef7-bc1e-9ca8f97278c3/api_function_public.png\" alt=\"Public function\" loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Public function\" convert=\"false\" width=\"18\" /\u003e \u003cimg src=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/fd4d5c72-a5e0-4857-9c34-796ea6c38d4a/api_function_static.png\" alt=\"Static\" loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Static\" convert=\"false\" width=\"18\" /\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003evoid\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/documentation/en-us/unreal-engine/API/Plugins/ChaosClothAsset/ChaosClothAsset/FClothGeometryTools/DeleteSimMesh\"\u003eDeleteSimMesh\u003c/a\u003e\n (\nconst TSharedRef\u003c FManagedArrayCollection \u003e\u0026 ClothCollection\u003cbr\u003e\n )\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eDelete the sim mesh data.\u003c/td\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/3d203a60-4729-4e5b-bf07-e31b66cbbfc5/api_function_public.png\" alt=\"Public function\" loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Public function\" convert=\"false\" width=\"18\" /\u003e \u003cimg src=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/ce932fe0-469f-4ffa-b2a8-ad15fe7003f9/api_function_static.png\" alt=\"Static\" loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Static\" convert=\"false\" width=\"18\" /\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003evoid\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/documentation/en-us/unreal-engine/API/Plugins/ChaosClothAsset/ChaosClothAsset/FClothGeometryTools/DeleteTethers\"\u003eDeleteTethers\u003c/a\u003e\n (\nconst TSharedRef\u003c FManagedArrayCollection \u003e\u0026 ClothCollection\u003cbr\u003e\n )\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eRemove all tethers.\u003c/td\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/51b8495c-595b-4c3d-ac5a-c3c291790853/api_function_public.png\" alt=\"Public function\" loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Public function\" convert=\"false\" width=\"18\" /\u003e \u003cimg src=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/60e85367-1e74-4eb8-9b51-bdabfee57b7e/api_function_static.png\" alt=\"Static\" loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Static\" convert=\"false\" width=\"18\" /\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eTSet\u003c int32 \u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/documentation/en-us/unreal-engine/API/Plugins/ChaosClothAsset/ChaosClothAsset/FClothGeometryTools/GenerateKinemati-\"\u003eGenerateKinematicVertices3D\u003c/a\u003e\n (\nconst TSharedRef\u003c FManagedArrayCollection \u003e\u0026 ClothCollection,\u003cbr\u003e\nconst FName\u0026 MaxDistanceMap,\u003cbr\u003e\nconst FVector2f\u0026 MaxDistanceValues,\u003cbr\u003e\nconst FName\u0026 InputKinematicVertices,\u003cbr\u003e\nfloat KinematicDistanceThreshold\u003cbr\u003e\n )\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eGenerate KinematicVertices3D set from the given MaxDistance weight map, MaxDistance values, and any additional kinematic vertices.\u003c/td\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/6142163d-abea-48cc-8456-d621df218974/api_function_public.png\" alt=\"Public function\" loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Public function\" convert=\"false\" width=\"18\" /\u003e \u003cimg src=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/cf1e1918-1fc9-4477-af05-29e3cce12ac1/api_function_static.png\" alt=\"Static\" loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Static\" convert=\"false\" width=\"18\" /\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003ebool\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/documentation/en-us/unreal-engine/API/Plugins/ChaosClothAsset/ChaosClothAsset/FClothGeometryTools/HasRenderMesh\"\u003eHasRenderMesh\u003c/a\u003e\n (\nconst TSharedRef\u003c const FManagedArrayCollection \u003e\u0026 ClothCollection\u003cbr\u003e\n )\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eReturn whether at least one pattern of this collection has any faces to render.\u003c/td\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/a4aa9e87-c41c-49dd-9246-3a47cbd44374/api_function_public.png\" alt=\"Public function\" loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Public function\" convert=\"false\" width=\"18\" /\u003e \u003cimg src=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/07b3c8d9-0a7c-4ab3-97d7-682da718fe74/api_function_static.png\" alt=\"Static\" loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Static\" convert=\"false\" width=\"18\" /\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003ebool\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/documentation/en-us/unreal-engine/API/Plugins/ChaosClothAsset/ChaosClothAsset/FClothGeometryTools/HasSimMesh\"\u003eHasSimMesh\u003c/a\u003e\n (\nconst TSharedRef\u003c const FManagedArrayCollection \u003e\u0026 ClothCollection\u003cbr\u003e\n )\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eReturn whether at least one pattern of this collection has any faces to simulate.\u003c/td\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/b3adece2-5097-41ad-b290-3134609c3e97/api_function_public.png\" alt=\"Public function\" loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Public function\" convert=\"false\" width=\"18\" /\u003e \u003cimg src=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/917db768-a7f3-4db3-95f6-7a96fc427ef0/api_function_static.png\" alt=\"Static\" loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Static\" convert=\"false\" width=\"18\" /\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003evoid\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/documentation/en-us/unreal-engine/API/Plugins/ChaosClothAsset/ChaosClothAsset/FClothGeometryTools/ReverseMesh\"\u003eReverseMesh\u003c/a\u003e\n (\nconst TSharedRef\u003c FManagedArrayCollection \u003e\u0026 ClothCollection,\u003cbr\u003e\nbool bReverseSimMeshNormals,\u003cbr\u003e\nbool bReverseSimMeshWindingOrder,\u003cbr\u003e\nbool bReverseRenderMeshNormals,\u003cbr\u003e\nbool bReverseRenderMeshWindingOrder,\u003cbr\u003e\nconst TArray\u003c int32 \u003e\u0026 SimPatternSelection,\u003cbr\u003e\nconst TArray\u003c int32 \u003e\u0026 RenderPatternSelection\u003cbr\u003e\n )\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eReverse the mesh normals. Will reverse all normals if pattern selection is empty.\u003c/td\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/2eb982c8-f43a-4817-ab9e-a84797ab680c/api_function_public.png\" alt=\"Public function\" loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Public function\" convert=\"false\" width=\"18\" /\u003e \u003cimg src=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/61d64ee7-575e-4f14-9986-0e36298a8b3d/api_function_static.png\" alt=\"Static\" loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Static\" convert=\"false\" width=\"18\" /\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003evoid\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/documentation/en-us/unreal-engine/API/Plugins/ChaosClothAsset/ChaosClothAsset/FClothGeometryTools/SampleVertices\"\u003eSampleVertices\u003c/a\u003e\n (\nconst TConstArrayView\u003c FVector3f \u003e VertexPositions,\u003cbr\u003e\nfloat CullDiameterSq,\u003cbr\u003e\nTSet\u003c int32 \u003e\u0026 OutVertexSet\u003cbr\u003e\n )\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eUse Poisson disk sampling to get a set of evenly-spaced vertices\u003c/td\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/d4a86cf4-9cb0-4aab-a516-c5406d126b7e/api_function_public.png\" alt=\"Public function\" loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Public function\" convert=\"false\" width=\"18\" /\u003e \u003cimg src=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/8d9bc836-c841-4fd1-98cd-a22fbfe08970/api_function_static.png\" alt=\"Static\" loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Static\" convert=\"false\" width=\"18\" /\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003evoid\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/documentation/en-us/unreal-engine/API/Plugins/ChaosClothAsset/ChaosClothAsset/FClothGeometryTools/TransferWeightMap\"\u003eTransferWeightMap\u003c/a\u003e\n (\nconst TConstArrayView\u003c FVector3f \u003e\u0026 SourcePositions,\u003cbr\u003e\nconst TConstArrayView\u003c FIntVector3 \u003e\u0026 InSourceIndices,\u003cbr\u003e\nconst TConstArrayView\u003c float \u003e\u0026 SourceWeights,\u003cbr\u003e\nconst TConstArrayView\u003c FVector3f \u003e\u0026 TargetPositions,\u003cbr\u003e\nconst TConstArrayView\u003c FVector3f \u003e\u0026 TargetNormals,\u003cbr\u003e\nconst TConstArrayView\u003c FIntVector3 \u003e\u0026 InTargetIndices,\u003cbr\u003e\nconst TArrayView\u003c float \u003e\u0026 TargetWeights\u003cbr\u003e\n )\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eTransfer a vertex weight map from a source to target mesh\u003c/td\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n  \u003c/tbody\u003e\n\u003c/table\u003e\n",
